      "comment_id" : 51027748,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "A note on performance: <code>isEmpty()</code> checks the internal length of an private array whereas <code>equals(Object anObject)</code> does much more (e.g. checking <code>instanceof</code>). Perfromance-wise, <code>isEmpty()</code> is generally faster."
    } ],
